data.description: An adorable 3 bedroom, plus loft area, 2.5 bath home conveniently located to dining and shopping; one mile to Downtown Woodstock and about a quarter mile to the Woofstock Dog Park and Greenway system connecting to Downtown Woodstock. This home offers the primary bedroom on main with walk-in closet, new flooring and updated ensuite bathroom with soaking tub and double vanity. The two story family room with fireplace opens to a dine-in kitchen, which has granite countertops, new stainless-steel appliances, including refrigerator, two pantries, and a breakfast bar island.  There are two (2) additional bedrooms,  a loft area, and full bath upstairs, and the washer/dryer is located upstairs. A large storage area is accessible through the upstairs bedroom.  As a bonus there is new interior paint throughout.  The privately fenced back yard is great for entertaining by the firepit on the large patio.
